      "actionDate": "2025-01-28",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Nutria Eradication and Control Reauthorization Act of 2025</strong></p><p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2030 the Nutria Eradication and Control Act of 2003, which allows the Department of the Interior to provide financial assistance to states for (1)&nbsp;eradicating or controlling nutria, and (2) restoring marshland damaged by nutria.&nbsp;Nutria are invasive, semi-aquatic rodents.</p>",
      "updateDate": "2025-02-05T20:53:11Z",
